BT /F1 10 Tf 54 738.00 Td (- It is message and event oriented. Events carry `std::unique_ptr<Message>`) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 724.00 Td (  and handlers use `std::function`. That is too heavy for per-instruction,) Tj ET
