BT /F1 10 Tf 54 682.00 Td (  fine for fabric and coarse subsystems, but awkward for tightly coupled GPU) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 668.00 Td (  internals with same-cycle or effectively zero-latency interactions.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 654.00 Td (- Conservative LBTS plus timestamp advances works best when there is real) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 640.00 Td (  lookahead. GPUs have many tiny-latency, high-frequency interactions. If) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 626.00 Td (  Mirage models compute units, schedulers, LDS, cache slices, and scoreboards) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 612.00 Td (  too finely as separate partitions, barrier and null-message overhead will) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 598.00 Td (  dominate.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 584.00 Td (- Mirage today is a direct functional simulator with queue submission, memory,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 570.00 Td (  decode cache, and compiled interpreter flow. Replacing that with per-event) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 556.00 Td (  PDES would likely regress functional-mode speed.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 534.00 Td (Because of that, Mirage should not:) Tj ET
